<L>__{exterior paris street day}
<A>__{an anonymous man agent 3 walks down a shabby paris street. stops before a small anonymous house. knocks.}
<L>__{interior paris house day}
<A>__{the anonymous man is let into the house by a figure we don't yet see. he looks round the room. a fire burning in the grate. english books on the table. a half eaten meal.}
<C>__{agent 3}
<D>__{i come from your brother.}
<A>__{now we see who he speaks to: william.}
<C>__{william}
<D>__{what does he want?}
<C>__{agent 3}
<D>__{he asks your forgiveness.}
<C>__{william}
<D>__{my forgiveness?}
<A>__{on william: he stares. then he understands. fear brings sudden tears to his eyes. a gasp. walsingham's man has plunged a knife into his heart.}
